<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">When disaster strikes, coming together as a community makes all the difference. After Hurricane Milton devastated the Clearwater area, many local residents found themselves displaced and without basic necessities. At one apartment building, over 500 people were rescued and evacuated as flooding destroyed their homes.</p>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">In response, Teamwork Commerce stepped in to lend a helping hand. We donated diapers, toiletries, and backpacks to support those affected by this tragedy, providing essential items to help them begin to rebuild their lives.</p>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">At Teamwork Commerce, we understand the importance of giving back, especially in times of need. We are proud to support our community and stand by our neighbors as they recover from this challenging event.</p>
<p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px;">Together, we can weather any storm.</p>
